radix 1 1 1 1 1 1 1
io i i i i i i i
vname decoder_en write_data pre_en write_enable read_en pre_en_SA sense_en
tunit 1ps
trise 5
tfall 5
vih 1.0
vil 0.0

* NOTE: pre_en, read_en, and pre_en_SA are assumed Active-LOW (0=ON, 1=OFF).
* decoder_en, write_enable, sense_en are assumed Active-HIGH (1=ON, 0=OFF).
*
* Time || dec_en || w_data || pre_en || w_en || read_en || preSA || sense_en

* 0. INITIALIZE (Precharge BL and SA)
0         0         0         0         0       1          0        0

* 1. WRITE '1' (Turn off precharge, assert WL and WE)
200       1         1         1         1       1          1        0

* 2. END WRITE (Turn off WL/WE, turn precharge back on)
600       0         1         0         0       1          0        0

* 3. READ '1' (Turn off precharge, turn on Read path, assert WL)
1000      1         0         1         0       0          1        0

* 4. SENSE (Wait for BL/BLb delta, then assert sense_en, turn off WL)
1200      0         0         1         0       0          1        1

* 5. END READ (Turn off sense, turn precharge back on)
1400      0         0         0         0       1          0        0

* 6. WRITE '0' (Turn off precharge, assert WL and WE)
1800      1         0         1         1       1          1        0

* 7. END WRITE (Turn off WL/WE, turn precharge back on)
2200      0         0         0         0       1          0        0

* 8. READ '0' (Turn off precharge, turn on Read path, assert WL)
2600      1         0         1         0       0          1        0

* 9. SENSE (Wait for BL/BLb delta, then assert sense_en, turn off WL)
2800      0         0         1         0       0          1        1

* 10. END SIMULATION (Turn off sense, turn precharge back on)
3000      0         0         0         0       1          0        0
